      <title>以色列通过有争议的法律来影响法官选择</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/israel-passes-controversial-law-to-influence-judge-selection</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列议会周四在周四凌晨通过了一项法律，增加了政客在选拔法官（包括向最高法院）中扮演的角色，引起了反对派领导人对他们认为对民主和团结的威胁的愤怒批评。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/israel-passes-controversial-law-to-influence-judge-selection</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 06:49:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国四月份针对汽车制造商采取紧急措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/south-korea-to-unveil-emergency-measures-for-automakers-in-april</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国高级贸易官员表示，政府将在下个月之前提出步骤，以帮助汽车行业，此前他早些时候与企业领袖召开了紧急会议，讨论了新的25％的美国汽车进口税率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/south-korea-to-unveil-emergency-measures-for-automakers-in-april</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 06:19:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
